data.description: Step right into your dream home at 331 Leonard Avenue! This home, situated in Westerleigh, a highly-sought out and in-demand neighborhood in Staten Island, will make you check off all of your dream home boxes! As you enter this cape-style home, you'll be instantly impressed with the open floor plan and beautiful hardwood floors. Walk right into the formal dining room and living room, with tons of natural light. The newly updated kitchen is complete with a farmhouse sink and stainless steel appliances. Situated next to the kitchen is the updated powder room. On the first level, there are three bedrooms, including the master bedroom with a door that leads directly to the yard outside. Upstairs, you'll find two generously-sized bedrooms and an additional storage room. The full basement and two-car garage will provide you with all the storage space you could ever need! There is a long driveway, and plenty of off-street parking. This home features a water filtering system, which promotes healthy living by removing impurities from your tap water. From the basement, you can access the outdoor space with a deck, grassy and concrete area, and even pear and fruit trees! With easy access and convenience of the location, your commute to Brooklyn or Manhattan is simple with the expressway, Verrazano bridge, and nearby transportation. Shopping, restaurants, local cafes and attractions are within reach! You'll love calling this place your new home!
